Project description

botocore-stubs

Type annotations and code completion for botocore package.This package is a part of mypy_boto3_builder project.

  • botocore-stubs
    • Installation
    • Usage
    • Versioning
    • Support and contributing

Installation

python -m pip install botocore-stubs

Usage

Use mypy or pyright for type checking.

Versioning

botocore-stubs version is the same as related botocore version and followsPEP 440 format.

Support and contributing

Please reports any bugs or request new features inbotocore-stubs repository.
